      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "我真的很难昧着自己的良心去说谎",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是鉴于昨天冒犯了你，你要是真的想听谎话，我也可以勉强配合一下",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1771135581156883010.jpg]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以，你到底要说什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "你的意思就是我非常暴躁",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "你有没有觉得我们俩陷入了一种琼瑶式的对话？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "你无耻，你无理取闹",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "你才无耻，你才无理取闹",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "我突然觉得你真是个老人家了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "说的都是老梗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "经典咏流传！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "话说你知道还珠格格又要打算重播了吗？",
