      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "对！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "很多梗和热点其实根本没流传开",
