      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "有的人被骗就想手撕的那些诈骗商家",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "我是想起一个段子",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "大家看篮球的时候进了一个球yes",
