      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "11:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "对对对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不是喜欢他吗？还一直吐槽他",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "11:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "可能我乳追吧（bushi",
