      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "我希望我没有感觉。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "希望自己的心像钢铁一样，像个大女人一样，这才酷",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "心像钢铁一样，哪里酷了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有知觉，没有感受。不会难过，不会心痛",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "这才是真正的漠视自己的痛苦",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们永远不要漠视自己的痛苦好吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为最想抚平我们痛苦的人只有自己",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "你怎么又懂了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不懂，你根本没有这样的经历",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "我确实没有这样的经历啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是我我我们对痛苦的感受都是一样的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "很伤心，喘不上气，觉得心脏要麻痹了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "真的？你是因为什么事呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "我是因为和家里人吵架了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "你也没有逃离原生家庭吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "逃离原生家庭很难啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "这世上能有几个人真正的逃离了原生家庭？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "我之前伤心的时候就需要转移注意的方式",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "比如呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "你都会做什么呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "找朋友诉苦啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "喝酒，看电影",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "看脱口秀线下演出，看乐队现场",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "听emo的歌",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "想哭就哭，疯狂哭大哭",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "这样能有用吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为在人群中难过是很有用的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "听到身边的人吵吵闹闹",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "我会好受一些",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "推荐你也试试",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "可身边人都不懂我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "让他们觉得我矫情，这样我就越来越孤独了，怎么办呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "你觉得我有觉得你矫情吗？",
